BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:Community
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a shared pause in the middle of a shifting moment—a
 n opportunity to ground ourselves in the longer history of belonging work i
 n higher education and imagine what this chapter might still hold. Together
 \, we’ll explore how past eras navigated pressure\, backlash\, and change\,
  and consider what patterns of resilience and creativity might illuminate o
 ur present. This is a dialogue\, not a debate—designed for listening\, refl
 ection\, and meaning-making across different roles\, experiences\, and pers
 pectives. You are welcome to arrive when you can\, leave when you need to\,
  and participate in the way that feels right for you. Come for connection\,
  context\, and the possibility that even now\, something new is waiting to 
 emerge.
DTEND:20260226T213000Z
DTSTAMP:20260314T021911Z
DTSTART:20260226T193000Z
