 aig-deforest
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:Lecture
DESCRIPTION:The n-body problem -\nIn this talk I will describe an old probl
 em from mechanics wherein we try to determine the future positions of n poi
 nt particles that interact only through the force of gravity.  I'll then sp
 ecialize to the 2-body or Kepler problem and survey some of the interesting
  mathematics that goes into the solution.
DTEND:20260227T003000Z
DTSTAMP:20260314T021911Z
DTSTART:20260226T234000Z
GEO:45.480972;-122.630792
LOCATION:Eliot Hall\, 314
