DESCRIPTION:On Friday 2/27 and Friday 3/6\, the Care Team will be hosting a
 n all-day\, drop-in support space (in person and virtual) for students who 
 want to read their Week 4 comments with a calm\, supportive staff member ne
 arby. Consider us your accountability-buddy or just someone to body double 
 with. \n\nIf opening feedback feels overwhelming\, sparks anxiety\, or lead
 s to “I’ll deal with this later” energy\, this space is for you. A Care Tea
 m staff member can sit with you while you read your comments\, help you tal
 k through what you’re feeling\, and support you in figuring out next steps…
 like reaching out to a faculty member\, connecting with tutoring\, or makin
 g a plan for the rest of the semester.\n\nThis is a low-pressure\, non-judg
 mental space designed to help you take that first step without spiraling. Y
 ou can come alone or with a friend to this shared space where others have t
 he same goal of getting support and finishing out the school year strong. \
 n\nStop by anytime on ✨February 27th or March 6th from 9am - 4:30pm\,🌟 even
