CATEGORIES:Community
DESCRIPTION:First Saturday PDX and Northwest China Council invite you to th
 e following program: Kang You Wei:  A Chinese Reformer in AmericaJane Leung
  Larson\n7 March\, 2026     9:30 - 11 am  Jane Larson will give an overview
  of her 2025 co-authored book\, "A Chinese Reformer in Exile\," which exami
 nes Kang Youwei’s travels in North America and leadership of the Chinese Em
 pire Reform Association between 1899 and 1911\, during his exile from China
  after the failed Hundred Days’ Reform of 1898.  Tracing his activities bet
 ween 1899 and 1911\, the global dimensions of this pioneering Chinese refor
 m movement will be highlighted with its impact on overseas Chinese communit
 ies\, including Portland\, one of the most active chapters of the reform as
 sociation.
DTEND:20260307T190000Z
DTSTAMP:20260314T021911Z
