 laying piano for the Portland Gay Men’s Chorus\, hosting a sing-along piano
  bar\, releasing albums\, performing on All Classical\, or one of his count
 less other piano endeavors\, he can be seen performing all across the count
 ry as Liberace. His attention to detail\, witty and humorous stage persona\
 , and spectacular piano performance has David in demand in venues from coas
 t to coast.\n\nMore details at oregonbravo.org/sequins
