DESCRIPTION:Were you inspired by the athletes competing this year during th
 e Olympics in Milan? Well\, you’re in luck! The Backpack Co-Op will be host
 ing its own Olympic Events on March 13th from 4:00 - 7:00 PM! \n\n \n\nTher
 e will be an official opening ceremony\, a variety of fun\, outdoors-themed
  events\, the chance to win prizes\, European-inspired snacks\, and much mo
 re excitement. Prizes include a chance to win a lightly used snowboard and 
 boots\, a guaranteed spot on an ROC trip\, and exclusive Backpack Co-Op mer
 ch! \n\n \n\nUnlike the actual Olympics\, you don’t need to come with a tea
 m\, and you don't need any experience. Just stop by\, experience some fun a
 nd chaos\, eat some delicious Italian food\, and become a bona fide Olympia
 n!
