DESCRIPTION:Mourning the bus cuts\nPoems on public transit\nJoyous little j
 aunt\n\nWere you intrigued by the transit haiku? Do you want free food? And
  community? And a bus adventure?\n\nJoin Reed sustainability in exploring t
 he TriMet bus system and building relations to place through creative writi
