LOCATION:Performing Arts Building\, Diver Studio Theatre
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:As You Like It
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_52066160159733
URL:https://events.reed.edu/event/as-you-like-it
END:VEVENT
